        {
            "title": "油價低收約2.4%　美伊或達成核協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英美期油低收約2.4%，連跌兩日。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094825_OilPrice_AP_source-ap_-2-1-1-1-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230711-094825_OilPrice_AP_source-ap_-2-1-1-1-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油收報61.62美元，跌1.53美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收報每桶64.53美元，跌1.56美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市場預期美國與伊朗將達成核協議，從而導致美國放鬆對伊朗的制裁，或為全球帶來額外原油供應，不利油價表現。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14932936-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e7%b4%842-4%e3%80%80%e7%be%8e%e4%bc%8a%e6%88%96%e9%81%94%e6%88%90%e6%a0%b8%e5%8d%94%e8%ad%b0",
